Pico 2 active firmware: copper puzzle and final puzzle piece.

This folder is the active Pico 2 project. The old dowels/wine puzzle code is archived in:

../../pico6-unused-future-puzzles/unused-future-puzzles/

Hardware:
- GPIO 15: copper puzzle complete contact
- GPIO 16: final puzzle piece placed contact

Main topics:
- Publishes escape/pico2/copper_puzzle_complete
- Publishes escape/pico2/final_piece_placed
- Subscribes escape/cmd/pico2/enable_copper_puzzle
- Subscribes escape/cmd/all/status_request
- Subscribes escape/cmd/all/reset_puzzle
